'''Siolu Sporipri''' was the mayor of [[Lagabee]], [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]] of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Ord Tiddell/Legends|Ord Tiddell]] in [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]]. He saw to its evacuation along with four million of its residents while [[Stone mite/Legends|stone mites]] consumed the city.

